items.title: Awesome Sitecore
items.content_text:
### Demo

*   [Sitecore Developer Portal (‚≠ê32)](https://github.com/Sitecore/developer-portal) - The Sitecore developer portal is built with Next.js, Typescript, and Tailwind CSS, and is hosted on Vercel. It uses static site generation (SSG) to create all the pages at build time. It also utilizes Incremental Static Regeneration (ISR) to automatically update the app when changes to page content are made. Many pages are written in Markdown and converted to HTML at build time. Images that are used are managed in Sitecore DAM and are published to a CDN.
items.content_html:
Demo

  • Sitecore Developer Portal (‚≠ê32) - The Sitecore developer portal is built with Next.js, Typescript, and Tailwind CSS, and is hosted on Vercel. It uses static site generation (SSG) to create all the pages at build time. It also utilizes Incremental Static Regeneration (ISR) to automatically update the app when changes to page content are made. Many pages are written in Markdown and converted to HTML at build time. Images that are used are managed in Sitecore DAM and are published to a CDN.
